entries.title_d: Track down an errant Naboo Diplomatic Corps craft and uncover what their cargo is.
entries.title: Naboo System: Discover the Naboo Diplomatic Corps Cargo
entries.split_quest_alert: \#pcontrast3 RSF Command: < \#pcontrast1 We are decoding the information you took from that NDC craft now.  Travel to Lok Space, we need you to meet up with one of our fighters for a quick delivery. \#pcontrast3 >
entries.quest_location_d: A location in the Naboo System
entries.quest_inspect_d: While you have the objective craft targeted, use /inspect command to determine their cargo.
entries.quest_dock_d: If the craft you have inspected containes the cargo you need, use the default '[' or ']' keys to cycle through their components to the engine slot.  After disabling the craft, pull up close and use the /dock command to retreive the cargo.
